But.

282
00:15:30,680 --> 00:15:32,240
I've never been in a relationship.

283
00:15:34,360 --> 00:15:36,080
I don't know what being in love feels like.

284
00:15:37,930 --> 00:15:43,450
♪ Old playlist's on replay,
get it then regret comes late ♪

285
00:15:45,220 --> 00:15:48,736
♪ The goodnight you said,
the small talks before sleep ♪

286
00:15:48,760 --> 00:15:50,950
♪ Turned into hopes
left hanging halfway ♪

287
00:15:51,590 --> 00:15:58,260
♪ Insomnia visits again,
thoughts wander close to my pillow ♪

288
00:15:58,490 --> 00:16:01,640
♪ We rely on touch and warmth,
just instinct to stay close ♪

289
00:16:01,920 --> 00:16:05,290
♪ Copying and imitating,
testing hearts in silent greed ♪

290
00:16:07,440 --> 00:16:08,976
Do you get it now?

291
00:16:09,000 --> 00:16:12,286
♪ The farther we walk to the other end ♪

292
00:16:12,310 --> 00:16:15,420
♪ Scars betray, brave drowned in floods ♪

293
00:16:15,790 --> 00:16:19,130
♪ When bringing up this part again ♪

294
00:16:19,870 --> 00:16:23,250
♪ It'll end before we notice ♪

295
00:16:39,520 --> 00:16:42,660
♪ Mist coils around the sleeping forest ♪

296
00:16:43,140 --> 00:16:46,320
♪ Memories scattered
through cracks of darkness ♪

297
00:16:46,680 --> 00:16:50,160
♪ How to escape this real-feeling dream ♪

298
00:16:53,710 --> 00:16:56,960
♪ Lies reflect in water's gleam ♪

299
00:16:57,190 --> 00:17:00,530
♪ Traces of existence
can never be erased ♪

300
00:17:00,810 --> 00:17:04,090
♪ How to find the self I can't reclaim ♪

301
00:17:06,410 --> 00:17:13,470
♪ Fly away, hear she says ♪

302
00:17:13,550 --> 00:17:17,506
♪ She'll fly out from
thorns of woven lies ♪

303
00:17:17,530 --> 00:17:21,106
♪ Pierce the fog,
shatter this dream tonight ♪

304
00:17:21,130 --> 00:17:24,066
♪ Burn like fire ♪

305
00:17:24,090 --> 00:17:27,510
♪ Just burn like fire ♪

306
00:17:27,730 --> 00:17:31,610
♪ The maze in the abyss starts to clear ♪

307
00:17:31,650 --> 00:17:34,336
♪ Yet night keep on whispering ♪

308
00:17:34,360 --> 00:17:37,500
♪ Surrender to fate,
no clear direction ahead ♪

309
00:17:37,780 --> 00:17:41,280
♪ She will rise as the dawn
that breaks the darkness ♪

310
00:17:41,360 --> 00:17:47,810
♪ Never slowing down,
for tomorrow cannot be stopped ♪

311
00:17:48,470 --> 00:17:51,786
♪ Surrender to love and find the way ♪

312
00:17:51,810 --> 00:17:55,330
♪ Even if fate tries to forget her ♪

313
00:17:55,550 --> 00:18:02,080
♪ Never despair,
for the heart burns with endless light ♪

314
00:18:02,490 --> 00:18:04,350
♪ Waiting for dawn ♪

